reviewText: Im in to African movies, this is a good one
Enjoyed watching this African comedy. Interesting cultural content. Couldn't wait to see part two. I hope there will be another in this series.

This DVD is awesome. It's truly about faith and regardless of your circumstances, stay true to God and He will bless you tenfold. I cried, I was able to relate to the issue within the movie and I praised God for faithfulness. In the end,  Faith Matters. Excellent for those who are going through issues with people you trust. Faith Matters!
